OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain or drizzle. Mainly dry
OL,7,Fin the afternoon but a few showers
OL,8,Fwill develop over Argyll. Some bright
OL,9,Fspells coming through later in the
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fevening with a few light showers
OL,14,Faround. Showers dying out overnight
OL,15,Fwith some clear spells developing.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FDry through the morning with
OL,18,Fgood sunny spells. Turning cloudy with
OL,19,Fsome showers spreading east through
OL,20,Fthe afternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
