OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fmixture of sunshine and showers on
OL,7,FTuesday and Wednesday. Longer spells
OL,8,Fof rain possible on Thursday. Feeling
OL,9,Frather cool for the time of year.
